description:
Create TypeScript type definitions for Cloudflare Worker environment bindings and shared API types.

## Requirements

- Define Env interface with all Cloudflare bindings:
  - D1Database for main database
  - KVNamespace for sessions
  - R2Bucket for file storage (future)
  - Environment variables (secrets, config)
- Define Variables interface for Hono context
- Export common API response types
- Export pagination types

## File Location
`packages/api/src/types/index.ts`

## Type Definitions
```typescript
interface Env {
  DB: D1Database;
  SESSION_KV: KVNamespace;
  STORAGE: R2Bucket;
  GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID: string;
  GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET: string;
  SESSION_SECRET: string;
  ALLOWED_ORIGINS: string;
}

interface Variables {
  user: Session | null;
}
```

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Env interface includes all Cloudflare bindings
- [ ] Variables interface for Hono context is defined
- [ ] Common response types are exported
- [ ] All types are properly exported
- [ ] TypeScript compiles without errors
